Spiders of Fangorn are clearly no better than spiders anywhere in Middle-earth. They are evil, and must be slain at any cost.

Fangorn Spinners can be found in the Silkenhold of Fangorn, far in the north of the forest's eaves.\n\nYou should defeat many Spinners in the Silkenhold, where spiders are clearly the greatest threat.
